---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="DevPlaybook privacy policy — how we handle your data, cookies, and analytics."
  noindex={false}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 15, 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        DevPlaybook (<a href="https://devplaybook.cc" class="text-primary hover:underline">devplaybook.cc</a>) is a free developer tool platform operated by an independent team. We provide browser-based developer tools, curated software resources, and technical blog content.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">What Data We Collect</h2>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-text">Tools Usage</h3>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
        All developer tools on DevPlaybook run <strong class="text-text">entirely in your browser</strong>. No data you enter into any tool (JSON, regex, code, etc.) is ever sent to our servers. We have no access to your tool input or output.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-text">Analytics</h3>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We use privacy-friendly analytics to understand which pages are visited and how the site performs. This data is aggregated and does not include personally identifiable information. We do not use Google Analytics.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-text">Newsletter</h3>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
        If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in every email. We do not share your email with third parties.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2 text-text">Cookies</h3>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        DevPlaybook uses minimal cookies for essential site functionality (e.g., theme preference, dismissed banners). Third-party services such as advertising partners may set their own cookies. You can control cookies through your browser settings.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">We may use the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-muted space-y-1">
        <li><strong class="text-text">Google AdSense</strong> — for displaying advertisements. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits. You can opt out at <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text">Gumroad</strong> — for processing purchases of premium products. Gumroad handles payment data under their own privacy policy.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text">Cloudflare</strong> — for hosting and CDN. Cloudflare may collect standard web server logs.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text">Buy Me a Coffee</strong> — for voluntary support. Handled under their own privacy policy.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-muted space-y-1">
        <li>To improve site performance and content</li>
        <li>To send newsletters you opted into</li>
        <li>To fulfill product purchases</li>
        <li>To display relevant advertisements</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Analytics data is retained in aggregated form. Newsletter subscriber data is retained until you unsubscribe. We do not store any tool usage data because it never leaves your browser.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        You have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal data we hold about you. To exercise these rights, contact us at the address below.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        DevPlaybook is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, please reach out via our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
